<p>Remember: the goal is to update this Subscription row to have the <em>new</em> <code>billingPeriodEndsAt</code>.
But the event's data doesn't have that date! No problem: if we fetch a fresh, full
<code>Subscription</code> object from Stripe's API, we can use its <code>current_period_end</code> field.</p>
